{"article_id":"4tbmALyt7PuT4cev","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"SEOUL , South Korea -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"North Korea has moved a missile with `` considerable range '' to its east coast ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"South Korea 's defense minister said Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"but he added","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that there are no signs","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"that the North is preparing for a full-scale conflict.","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Yet CNN reported early Thursday","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that a U.S. official says","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that the regime may be readying a missile launch.","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Communications intercepts in recent days indicated","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that Pyongyang could be planning to launch a mobile ballistic missile in the coming days or weeks ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"the official told CNN .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"It 's unknown","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"whether it would be a test or a strike.","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"South Korean Defense Minister Kim Kwan-jin told a parliamentary committee in Seoul","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that the North has moved a medium-range missile to its east coast for an imminent test firing or military drill.","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"The missile does n't appear to be aimed at the U.S. mainland ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Kim said ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"according to the semi-official South Korean news agency Yonhap.","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The report came","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"hours after North Korea 's military warned","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that it has been authorized to attack the U.S.","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"using `` smaller , lighter and diversified '' nuclear weapons .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"It was the North 's latest war cry against America in recent weeks .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"The reference to smaller weapons could be a claim","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"that North Korea has improved its nuclear technology , or a bluff.","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"The North is not believed to have mastered the technology","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"needed to miniaturize nuclear bombs enough","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"to mount them on long-range missiles.","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"South Korean Defense Minister Kim Kwan-jin said","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"he did not know the reasons behind the North 's missile movement ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and that it `` could be for testing or drills . ``","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"He dismissed reports in Japanese media","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"that the missile could be a KN-08 ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"which is believed to be a long-range missile","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"if operable","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"could hit the United States.","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"Kim told lawmakers at a parliamentary committee meeting","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"that the missile has `` considerable range ''","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"but not enough","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"to hit the U.S. mainland.","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"The range","depth":16},{"id":43,"text":"he described","depth":16},{"id":44,"text":"could refer to a mobile North Korean missile","depth":16},{"id":45,"text":"known as the Musudan ,","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"believed to have a range of 3,000 kilometers","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"( 1,800 miles ) .","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"That would make Japan and South Korea potential targets","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"- along with U.S. bases in both countries -","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"but there are doubts about the missile 's accuracy.","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"The Pentagon announced","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that it will hasten the deployment of a missile defense system to the U.S. Pacific territory of Guam","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to strengthen regional protection against a possible attack.","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Experts say","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"North Korea has not demonstrated","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that it has accurate long-range missiles .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Some suspect","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that an apparent long-range missile","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"unveiled by the North at a parade last year","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"was actually a mockup .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"`` From what we know of its existing inventory , North Korea has short- and medium-range missiles","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that could complicate a situation on the Korean Peninsula","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"( and perhaps reach Japan ) ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"but we have not seen any evidence","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that it has long-range missiles","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that could strike the continental U.S. , Guam or Hawaii , ''","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"James Hardy , Asia Pacific editor of IHS Jane 's Defence Weekly , wrote in a recent analysis.","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"Kim , the South Korean defense minister , said","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"if North Korea were preparing for a full-scale conflict ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"there would be signs such as the mobilization of a number of units ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"including supply and rear troops ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"but South Korean military officials have found no such preparations .","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"`` ( North Korea 's recent threats ) are rhetorical threats .","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"I believe","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"the odds of a full-scale provocation are small , ''","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"But he added","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"that North Korea might mount a small-scale provocation such as its 2010 shelling of a South Korean island , an attack","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"that killed four people.","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"North Korea has been railing against joint U.S.-South Korean military exercises","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"that are taking place in South Korea","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"and has expressed anger over tightened U.N. sanctions for its February nuclear test .","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"Many of the threats come in the middle of the night in Asia","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"- daytime for the U.S. audience.","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"Analysts say","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"the threats are probably efforts","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"to provoke softer policies from South Korea ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"to win diplomatic talks with Washington","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"and to solidify the image of young North Korean leader Kim Jong Un.","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"At times , North Korea has gone beyond rhetoric.","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"On Tuesday , it announced","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"it would restart a plutonium reactor","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"it had shut down in 2007 .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"A U.S. research institute said Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"that satellite imagery shows","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"that construction","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"needed for the restart","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"has already begun.","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"For a second day Thursday , North Korean border authorities denied entry to South Koreans","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"who manage jointly run factories in the North Korean city of Kaesong .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"South Koreans already at the plant were being allowed to return home.","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"South Korea has prepared a military contingency plan","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"should North Korea hold South Korean workers hostage in Kaesong ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Defense Minister Kim said .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"He would n't elaborate.","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Outraged over comments in the South about possible hostage-taking and a military response from Seoul ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"a North Korean government-run committee threatened to pull North Korean workers out of Kaesong as well.","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"North Korea 's military statement Thursday , from an unnamed spokesman from the General Bureau of the Korean People 's Army , said","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"its troops had been authorized to counter U.S. `` aggression '' with `` powerful practical military counteractions , '' including nuclear weapons.","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"It said","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"America 's `` hostile policy '' and `` nuclear threat '' against North Korea `` will be smashed by the strong will of all the united service personnel and people and cutting-edge smaller , lighter and diversified nuclear strike means. ''","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"U.S . Defense Secretary Chuck Hagel said","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Washington is doing all","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"it can","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"to defuse the situation .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"`` Some of the actions","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"they 've taken over the last few weeks","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"present a real and clear danger and threat '' to the U.S. and its allies ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Hagel said Wednesday.","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"South Korea 's Defense Ministry said","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"its military is ready to deal with any provocation by North Korea .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"`` I can say","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"we have no problem in crisis management , ''","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"deputy ministry spokesman Wee Yong-sub told reporters.","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"The defense minister , however , was criticized by lawmakers over a North Korean defector","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"who stole a South Korean fishing boat Wednesday night","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"and fled back to North Korea across the western sea border.","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"Kim said","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"South Korean radar had a `` blind spot '' in the area","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and South Korean troops were unaware","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"the defector was fleeing","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"until he almost reached the North Korean side .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Lawmakers questioned his military 's readiness","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"to detect and counter enemy troops","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"who might use similar blind spots.","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"This spring 's annual U.S.-South Korea drills have incorporated fighter jets and nuclear-capable stealth bombers .","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"The allies insist","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"they are routine exercises .","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"North Korea calls them rehearsals for a northward invasion","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"and says","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"it needs nuclear weapons","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"to defend itself.","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"On Sunday , Kim Jong Un led a high-level meeting of party officials","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"who declared","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"building the economy and `` nuclear armed forces '' as the nation 's priorities.","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"North Korea is believed to be working toward building an atomic bomb","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"small enough","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"to mount on a long-range missile .","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"Long-range rocket launches","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"designed to send satellites into space in 2009 and 2012","depth":15},{"id":152,"text":"were widely considered covert tests of missile technology ,","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"and North Korea has conducted three underground nuclear tests .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"`` I do n't believe","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"North Korea has the capacity","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"to attack the United States with nuclear weapons","depth":17},{"id":157,"text":"mounted on missiles ,","depth":17},{"id":158,"text":"and wo n't for many years .","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"Its ability","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"to target and strike South Korea","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"is also very limited , ''","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"nuclear scientist Siegfried Hecker , a senior fellow at the Center for International Security and Cooperation at Stanford University , said this week.","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"In comments","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"posted on CISAC 's website ,","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"Hecker said","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"North Korea knows","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"a nuclear attack would be met with `` a devastating nuclear response . ``","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"Hecker has estimated","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"that North Korea has enough plutonium","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"to make several crude nuclear bombs .","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"Its announcement Tuesday","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"that it would restart a plutonium reactor","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"indicated","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"that it intends to produce more nuclear weapons material.","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"The U.S.-Korea Institute at Johns Hopkins School of Advanced International Studies has analyzed recent commercial satellite imagery of the Nyongbyon nuclear facility ,","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"where the reactor was shut down in 2007 under the terms of a disarmament agreement .","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"A cooling tower for the reactor was destroyed in 2008.","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"The analysis","depth":13},{"id":179,"text":"published Wednesday on the institute 's website , 38 North ,","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"says","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"that rebuilding the tower would take six months ,","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"but a March 27 photo shows","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"building work may have started for an alternative cooling system","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"that could take just weeks .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"Experts estimate","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"it could take three months to a year to restart the plant .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":373,"left":0,"right":372,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":372,"left":266,"right":371,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":253,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":239,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":199,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":191,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":188,"right":190,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":3,"right":189,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":193,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":6,"right":192,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":197,"left":195,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":194,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":196,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":235,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":203,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":200,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":201,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left